------------------------------------------------------------------------------
WHY THIS LICENSE
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Pyrochrome is trained on and derived from the Glazy public dataset
(https://github.com/derekphilipau/glazy-data), which is licensed under
CC BY-NC-SA 4.0. The ShareAlike clause requires derivative works to carry the
same license, and NonCommercial forbids commercial use. We therefore release
the whole project under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 to remain compliant.

See DATA.md for the full data provenance and attribution.
